[[Image:The New Princess and Girl - October 10 1964.gif|thumb|right|200px|The first issue to feature ''The Hobbit''.]]
'''Princess''', also known as '''The New Princess and Girl''', was a weekly magazine aimed at girls, published by Fleetway. From [[10 October]], [[1964]] to [[16 January]], [[1965]], it featured an abridged, fifteen part serialization of ''[[The Hobbit]]''. 

Each episode was published on two pages, and featured five images by [[Ferguson Dewar]].
